{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":905,"text":"I am a climate scientist,"},{"time":3214,"text":"and I hate weather."},{"time":6001,"text":"I have spent too much time in California,"},{"time":8431,"text":"and I strongly feel that weather\nshould be optional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13278,"text":"So I don't want to experience clouds,"},{"time":16343,"text":"let alone study them."},{"time":18366,"text":"But clouds seem to follow me\nwherever I go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22822,"text":"The thing is, clouds are a real\nchallenge for climate science."},{"time":27971,"text":"We don't know how they're going to react\nas the planet heats up,"},{"time":31816,"text":"and hidden in that uncertainty"},{"time":35561,"text":"might be hope."},{"time":37531,"text":"Maybe, just maybe,"},{"time":40088,"text":"clouds could slow down global warming,"},{"time":42793,"text":"and buy us a little bit more time\nto get our act together,"},{"time":46464,"text":"which would be very convenient right now."},{"time":49600,"text":"I mean, even I could put up\nwith a few more cloudy days"},{"time":53714,"text":"if clouds saved the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56722,"text":"Now, we are sure about some things."},{"time":59897,"text":"Carbon dioxide is a greenhouse gas,"},{"time":62244,"text":"we're emitting a lot of it,"},{"time":63664,"text":"and the planet is heating up."},{"time":65534,"text":"Case closed."},{"time":67507,"text":"But I still go to work every day."},{"time":69970,"text":"It turns out that there is a lot\nthat we don't understand"},{"time":73694,"text":"about climate change."},{"time":75614,"text":"In particular, we haven't answered"},{"time":78102,"text":"what seems to be a very\nfundamental question."},{"time":81584,"text":"We know it's going to get hot,"},{"time":83199,"text":"but we don't know exactly\nhow hot it's going to get."},{"time":87672,"text":"Now, this is a really\neasy question to answer"},{"time":90635,"text":"if one of you would like\nto give me a time machine."},{"time":93633,"text":"But I'm going to be honest with you:"},{"time":96118,"text":"if I had a time machine,"},{"time":98197,"text":"I would not be hanging out\nat this particular point in history."},{"time":102229,"text":"So in order to see the future,"},{"time":105306,"text":"we have to rely on the output\nof computer simulations --"},{"time":108944,"text":"climate models, like this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111518,"text":"Now, in my line of work,"},{"time":113382,"text":"I encounter many very charming\npeople on the internet"},{"time":117107,"text":"who like to tell me\nthat climate models are all wrong."},{"time":121942,"text":"And I would just like to say:"},{"time":124282,"text":"no kidding!"},{"time":126389,"text":"Seriously? I get paid to complain\nabout climate models."},{"time":129991,"text":"But we don't want models to be perfect."},{"time":133825,"text":"We want them to be useful."},{"time":135946,"text":"I mean, think about it:"},{"time":137601,"text":"a computer simulation"},{"time":139683,"text":"that's able to exactly\nreproduce all of reality."},{"time":144166,"text":"That's not a climate model;"},{"time":146495,"text":"That's \"The Matrix.\""},{"time":149022,"text":"So, models are not crystal balls."},{"time":152458,"text":"They're research tools,"},{"time":154173,"text":"and the ways in which they're wrong\ncan actually teach us a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158993,"text":"For example:"},{"time":160370,"text":"different climate models\nare largely able to capture"},{"time":163388,"text":"the warming that we've seen so far."},{"time":165536,"text":"But fast-forward to the end of the century"},{"time":168328,"text":"under a business-as-usual scenario,"},{"time":170681,"text":"and climate models\ndon't really agree anymore."},{"time":173787,"text":"Yeah, they're all warming;\nthat's just basic physics."},{"time":177330,"text":"But some of them project catastrophe --"},{"time":180563,"text":"more than five times the warming\nwe've seen already."},{"time":183756,"text":"And others are literally more chill."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187019,"text":"So why don't climate models agree\non how warm it's going to get?"},{"time":192434,"text":"Well, to a large extent,"},{"time":194505,"text":"it's because they don't agree\non what clouds will do in the future."},{"time":198752,"text":"And that is because, just like me,"},{"time":201547,"text":"computers hate clouds."},{"time":203819,"text":"Computers hate clouds because\nthey're simultaneously very large"},{"time":208033,"text":"and very small."},{"time":209804,"text":"Clouds are formed"},{"time":210986,"text":"when microscopic water droplets\nor ice crystals coalesce"},{"time":215635,"text":"around tiny particles."},{"time":217695,"text":"But at the same time, they cover\ntwo-thirds of the earth's surface."},{"time":221895,"text":"In order to really\naccurately model clouds,"},{"time":224939,"text":"we'd need to track the behavior\nof every water droplet and dust grain"},{"time":229487,"text":"in the entire atmosphere,"},{"time":230953,"text":"and there's no computer\npowerful enough to do that."},{"time":233856,"text":"So instead, we have to make a trade-off:"},{"time":237120,"text":"we can zoom in and get the details right,"},{"time":240047,"text":"but have no idea\nwhat's going on worldwide;"},{"time":243049,"text":"or, we could sacrifice\nrealism at small scales"},{"time":247996,"text":"in order to see the bigger picture."},{"time":250309,"text":"Now, there's no one right answer,"},{"time":252563,"text":"no perfect way to do this,"},{"time":254602,"text":"and different climate models\nmake different choices."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258443,"text":"Now, it is unfortunate"},{"time":260832,"text":"that computers struggle with clouds,"},{"time":263194,"text":"because clouds are crucially important"},{"time":265916,"text":"in regulating the temperature\nof the planet."},{"time":268634,"text":"In fact, if all the clouds went away,"},{"time":271229,"text":"we would experience\nprofound climate changes."},{"time":274989,"text":"But without clouds,"},{"time":276486,"text":"would it be warmer or colder?"},{"time":279492,"text":"The answer is both."}]},{"cues":[{"time":282016,"text":"So I'm going to be honest with you,\nI am not a cloud spotter."},{"time":285062,"text":"My favorite type of cloud is none."},{"time":287770,"text":"But even I know that clouds\ncome in all shapes and sizes."},{"time":292567,"text":"Low, thick clouds like these\nare really good at blocking out the sun"},{"time":296811,"text":"and ruining your barbecue,"},{"time":298888,"text":"and high, wispy clouds like these cirrus"},{"time":301835,"text":"largely let that sunlight stream through."},{"time":304616,"text":"Every sunny day is the same,"},{"time":307037,"text":"but every cloudy day\nis cloudy in its own way."},{"time":310037,"text":"And it's this diversity"},{"time":312019,"text":"that can make the global impact of clouds\nvery hard to understand."},{"time":316276,"text":"So to see this global effect of clouds,"},{"time":319304,"text":"it really helps to take a selfie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323138,"text":"It will never cease to blow my mind"},{"time":326663,"text":"that we can see our planet\nfrom outer space,"},{"time":329872,"text":"but we can't see all of it."},{"time":332118,"text":"Clouds are blocking the view."},{"time":334300,"text":"That's what they do."},{"time":335689,"text":"These low, thick clouds\nare extremely effective sunshades."},{"time":340399,"text":"They turn back about 20 percent\nof everything the sun sends us."},{"time":344474,"text":"That is a lot of wasted solar power."},{"time":347202,"text":"So, low clouds are powerful sunshades,"},{"time":350208,"text":"making the planet cooler."},{"time":352072,"text":"But that's not the only effect of clouds."},{"time":354946,"text":"Our planet has a temperature,"},{"time":356542,"text":"and like anything with a temperature,"},{"time":358753,"text":"it's giving off heat."},{"time":360649,"text":"We are radiating thermal energy\naway into space,"},{"time":363999,"text":"and we can see this in the infrared."},{"time":366868,"text":"Once again, clouds are blocking the view."},{"time":370387,"text":"That's because high clouds live\nin the upper reaches of the atmosphere,"},{"time":374214,"text":"where it's very cold."},{"time":375991,"text":"And this means that they lose\nvery little heat to space themselves."},{"time":379713,"text":"But at the same time, they block\nthe heat coming up from the planet below."},{"time":384128,"text":"The earth is trying to cool itself off,"},{"time":387027,"text":"and high clouds are getting in the way."},{"time":390163,"text":"The result is a very\npowerful greenhouse effect."},{"time":394999,"text":"So, clouds play this very\nlarge and dual role"},{"time":398877,"text":"in the climate system."},{"time":400472,"text":"We've got low clouds that act\nlike a sunshade,"},{"time":403287,"text":"cooling the planet,"},{"time":404680,"text":"and high clouds which act\nlike a greenhouse,"},{"time":407623,"text":"warming the planet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409425,"text":"Right now, these two effects --\nthey don't cancel out."},{"time":412690,"text":"That sunshade -- it's a little\nbit more powerful."},{"time":416132,"text":"So if we got rid\nof all the clouds tomorrow,"},{"time":419234,"text":"which, for the record,\nI am not advocating,"},{"time":422472,"text":"our planet would get warmer."},{"time":425055,"text":"So clearly, all of the clouds\nare not going away."},{"time":428810,"text":"But climate change is change."},{"time":431528,"text":"So we can ask:"},{"time":432962,"text":"How will global warming change clouds?"},{"time":436876,"text":"But remember, clouds are so important"},{"time":439714,"text":"in regulating the earth's temperature,"},{"time":441836,"text":"and they both warm and cool the planet."},{"time":444571,"text":"So even small changes to cloud cover"},{"time":447675,"text":"could have profound consequences."},{"time":450240,"text":"So we might also ask:"},{"time":452224,"text":"How will clouds change global warming?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455970,"text":"And that is where there might\nbe space for hope."},{"time":459685,"text":"If global warming triggers cloud changes"},{"time":462913,"text":"that make for a less powerful greenhouse\nor a more effective sunshade,"},{"time":468089,"text":"then that would enhance\nthe cooling power of clouds."},{"time":471803,"text":"It would act in opposition\nto global warming,"},{"time":475354,"text":"and that's what's happening\nin those climate models"},{"time":478348,"text":"that project relatively muted warming."},{"time":481394,"text":"But climate models struggle with clouds,"},{"time":484781,"text":"and this uncertainty -- it goes both ways."},{"time":488592,"text":"Clouds could help us out\nwith global warming."},{"time":491833,"text":"They could also make it worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":494133,"text":"Now, we know that\nclimate change is happening"},{"time":497043,"text":"because we can see it:"},{"time":498832,"text":"rising temperatures, melting icecaps,\nshifts in rainfall patterns."},{"time":504881,"text":"And you might think that we\ncould also see it in the clouds."},{"time":508302,"text":"But here's something else unfortunate:"},{"time":510842,"text":"clouds are really hard to see."},{"time":514434,"text":"I see everybody from the Pacific Northwest"},{"time":516504,"text":"is like, \"I have some\nsuggestions for you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":518727,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519775,"text":"And you guys, we have tried looking up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522395,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523470,"text":"But in order to do climate science,"},{"time":526513,"text":"we need to see all of the clouds,\neverywhere, for a very long time."},{"time":531670,"text":"And that's what makes it hard."},{"time":534097,"text":"Now, nothing sees more clouds\nthan a satellite --"},{"time":538895,"text":"not even a British person."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540839,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541984,"text":"And fortunately, we do have\nsatellite observations of clouds"},{"time":547115,"text":"that, like me, date back to the 1980s."},{"time":550682,"text":"But these satellites\nwere designed for weather,"},{"time":554320,"text":"not climate."},{"time":555868,"text":"They weren't in it for the long haul."},{"time":557806,"text":"So to get that long-term\ntrend information,"},{"time":560516,"text":"we need to do climate science."},{"time":562315,"text":"We have to stitch together\nthe output of multiple satellites"},{"time":565457,"text":"with different viewing angles and orbits"},{"time":568559,"text":"and carrying different camera equipment."},{"time":570506,"text":"And as a result,"},{"time":571752,"text":"there are gaps in our knowledge."},{"time":574499,"text":"But even from this very cloudy picture,"},{"time":577852,"text":"we're starting to get hints\nof a possible future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581648,"text":"When we looked at the observations,"},{"time":584272,"text":"one thing jumped out at us:"},{"time":586672,"text":"the clouds are moving."},{"time":589693,"text":"As the planet's temperature increases,"},{"time":592206,"text":"high clouds rise up."},{"time":594686,"text":"They move to the colder\nupper reaches of the atmosphere,"},{"time":598940,"text":"and this means that even\nas the planet heats up,"},{"time":602627,"text":"high clouds don't."},{"time":604384,"text":"They remain at roughly\nthe same temperature."},{"time":607045,"text":"So they are not losing more heat to space."},{"time":610567,"text":"But at the same time,\nthey're trapping more heat"},{"time":613628,"text":"from the warming planet below."},{"time":615849,"text":"This intensifies the greenhouse effect."},{"time":619794,"text":"High clouds are making\nglobal warming worse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624382,"text":"Clouds are moving\nin other dimensions, too."},{"time":626871,"text":"The atmospheric circulation,\nthat large-scale motion"},{"time":629900,"text":"of air and water in the atmosphere,"},{"time":631842,"text":"is changing,"},{"time":633253,"text":"and clouds are going with it."},{"time":637216,"text":"On large scales,"},{"time":638846,"text":"clouds seem to be moving\nfrom the tropics toward the poles."},{"time":642982,"text":"It's kind of like your\ngrandparents in reverse."},{"time":646207,"text":"And this matters,"},{"time":647810,"text":"because if your job\nis to block incoming sunlight,"},{"time":651683,"text":"you are going to be much\nmore effective in the tropics"},{"time":654723,"text":"under that intense tropical sun"},{"time":656944,"text":"than you are in higher latitudes."},{"time":659272,"text":"So if this keeps up,"},{"time":661166,"text":"this will also make global warming worse."},{"time":664287,"text":"And what we have not found,"},{"time":666632,"text":"despite years of looking,"},{"time":668934,"text":"is any indication of the opposite."},{"time":672045,"text":"There is no observational evidence"},{"time":675001,"text":"that clouds will substantially\nslow down global warming."},{"time":680141,"text":"The earth is not going\nto break its own fever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684193,"text":"Now, there are still uncertainties here."},{"time":687224,"text":"We don't know for sure"},{"time":689476,"text":"what the future holds."},{"time":691851,"text":"But we are sending our kids there,"},{"time":694982,"text":"and they are never coming back."},{"time":698433,"text":"I want them to be prepared\nfor what they'll face,"},{"time":702300,"text":"and that is why it is so important"},{"time":705567,"text":"to keep our earth-observing\nsatellites up there"},{"time":708842,"text":"and to hire diverse and smart\nand talented people"},{"time":712662,"text":"who do not hate clouds"},{"time":714953,"text":"to improve the climate models."}]},{"cues":[{"time":717570,"text":"But uncertainty is not ignorance."},{"time":722053,"text":"We don't know everything,"},{"time":724093,"text":"but we don't know nothing,"},{"time":726434,"text":"and we know what carbon dioxide does."},{"time":729831,"text":"I started my career as an astrophysicist,"},{"time":733019,"text":"so you can believe me"},{"time":734525,"text":"when I say that this is the greatest\nplace in the universe."},{"time":741084,"text":"Other planets might have liquid water."},{"time":744988,"text":"On earth, we have whiskey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748155,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":750192,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":755224,"text":"We are so lucky to live here,"},{"time":759590,"text":"but let's not push our luck."},{"time":762476,"text":"I don't think that clouds\nwill save the planet."},{"time":766225,"text":"I think that's probably up to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768357,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":769620,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}